# output/ is untracked entirely (not just its *.nc contents) since on the HPC it's a symlink to scratch
# space -- git refuses to operate on tracked paths behind a symlinked directory ("beyond a symbolic link"
# fatal errors on stash/checkout/etc). A fresh checkout needs output/ created manually: `mkdir output` for
# local dev, or the scratch symlink dance documented in conversation history for the HPC.
/output/
